What you need to know:

Only players and their caddies, tournament officials and authorised media personnel will be allowed at Karen.Talking of the caddies, the Magical Kenya Open has usually been a harvesting time for the local caddies. However, due to the pandemic and World Health Organization protocols, the visiting professionals preferred to use the caddies they usually use in Europe and elsewhere.Thus a few caddies will have the opportunity of earning some cash by caddying for the local and regional players.